P2pool Stats Page Skin/Makeover

Trying to get Web interface on the P2Pool looking nice.

Not sure what the previous intention was, but here I will be messing around with HTML, CSS, Javascript from the standard distro to make a different looking skin for the web interface for P2Pool stats page.

27.01.2014 - Ver 0.1

First edit

To use/install:

1. Download the files from GitHub
2. Save "web-static" directory as "web-static-backup"
3. Create director "web-static"
4. Copy the downloaded files into the new directory "web-static" 

